body.p:
In some cases, when your document contains a lot of tracked changes, you may need to hide the
      footnotes associated with the insertions, deletions, or attribute changes. Using the following
      example, the deletions and insertions are hidden, but the comments remain visible. In your
        customization CSS,
      add:oxy-attributes,
oxy-delete,
oxy-insert{
  float:none;
  display:none;
}
